{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-project-js","path":"/portfolio/recent-posts-markdown-wordpress-plugin/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0c1018fb-6281-53a4-9988-293d5eda4a45","html":"<p>Cross Post Content from your WordPress blog to other platforms often? Then you should check out my Recent Posts Markdown Generator WordPress Plugin.</p>\n<div class=\"buttons\">\n<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/recent-posts-markdown/\" class=\"button\">Download The Plugin</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/harnerdesigns/recent-posts-md/\" class=\"button\">See The Source</a>\n</div>\n<p>I built this plugin out of necessity. I was cross posting a lot of articles to <a href=\"https://dev.to/jackharner\">Dev.to</a> and needed a quick and easy way to generate a list of Recent Post links back to my blog.</p>\n<p>Select the post type you wish to link, and how many posts to get and it outputs the following:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"markdown\"><pre class=\"language-markdown\"><code class=\"language-markdown\"><span class=\"token title important\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">##</span> Recent Posts</span>\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">*</span> <span class=\"token url\">[<span class=\"token content\">Something</span>](<span class=\"token url\">http://localhost/blank/projects/something/</span>)</span>\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">*</span> <span class=\"token url\">[<span class=\"token content\">Lololol</span>](<span class=\"token url\">http://localhost/blank/projects/lololol/</span>)</span>\n<span class=\"token list punctuation\">*</span> <span class=\"token url\">[<span class=\"token content\">Blah Blah Blah</span>](<span class=\"token url\">http://localhost/blank/projects/blah-blah-blah/</span>)</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"plugin-roadmap\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#plugin-roadmap\" aria-label=\"plugin roadmap permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Plugin Roadmap</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\"Skip most recent post\". I didn't want to link to the original post as the first item in the list. So, I'd end up getting 4 posts and then just deleting the first one. It'd save some time to just have that as an option.</li>\n<li>Link to multiple Post Types.</li>\n</ul>","wordCount":{"words":130},"frontmatter":{"title":"Recent Posts Markdown Generator","description":"WordPress Plugin","color":"#4e2ea1","date":"July 17, 2020","tags":["WordPress","PHP","Automation"],"images":[{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"constrained","backgroundColor":"#f8f8f8","images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/004e5/screenshot-with-markdown.png","srcSet":"/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/107ed/screenshot-with-markdown.png 200w,\n/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/9a6f9/screenshot-with-markdown.png 400w,\n/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/004e5/screenshot-with-markdown.png 800w,\n/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/f4261/screenshot-with-markdown.png 1600w","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/19d43/screenshot-with-markdown.webp 200w,\n/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/f9846/screenshot-with-markdown.webp 400w,\n/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/e9ef0/screenshot-with-markdown.webp 800w,\n/static/3ad781cbc52d56b875e35767c967c006/f3b93/screenshot-with-markdown.webp 1600w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"(min-width: 800px) 800px, 100vw"}]},"width":800,"height":421}}}],"